{"tid":1508673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一割蓆條件：破壞信任","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T15:05:24.000Z","uid":235552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecc5b38152d1ef27e5a4d5d6ed2c750a75be3be","tid":1508673,"uid":235552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"係我眼中信任既威力大過核彈，係人與人之間最基本亦最重要既部份<br />\n我地發展到今日，兄弟爬山各自努力都係建基於信任<br />\n我地connect到其他人，之間都存在住信任<br />\n<br />\n無左信任，我地之間就咩都斷晒<br />\n唔可以俾呢個缺口打開，係底線黎<br />\n<br />\n假消息fake news會傷害到我地甚至本來connect到既外人對我地既信任，就算俾你一兩次過到骨，咁日後仲有幾多呢啲fake news？邊一次會俾人用黎大造文章？<br />\n破壞信任之後我地之間只會越黎越多磨擦，會走向失敗<br />\n<br />\n1999 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15411d7761e48fe74803ff771bb5603be7229a42","tid":1508673,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"434938a468246cb1fbe57915e9517dde44eed45e","tid":1508673,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=48f07003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2